    "description": "One of the strongest men ever graduated from the College leaves this year to accept a position with the Civil Service Commission as industrial teacher in the Philippines. He came to the College in the year 1902 and was graduated from the Mechanical Department in 1907. This year while serving in the capacity of assistant in Mechanical Engineering, he has also worked out an M. S. M. E., taking as his subject, \"A Complete Efficiency Test of the Mechanical Engineering Department of the College.\" In all student organizations and especially in athletics has not only taken an active part, but has usually been a leader.",
    "image": "New Mexico State University_1908_页面_01.png"
  },
